      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To establish a special enrollment period for family members of an individual who has died by suicide, to establish a competitive grant program to provide services and support to friends and family members impacted by an individual's suicide, and for other purposes.</title>
